Czech PX50 closes slightly lower . The Czech PX50 again closed down on Monday with turnover staying low and major issues showing no sign of a turnaround . The PX50 dropped 0 . 6 percent to 535 . 4 while the major issue dominated RPIX fell by the same amount to 1 , 117 . 4 . Zivnostenska Banka was one of the biggest decliners , dropped 130 crowns , 4 . 9 percent , to 2 , 480 after posting audited 1996 net profits of 378 million crowns down from 406 million crowns the year before . The figures were calculated according to international accounting standards . - - Robin Shepherd , Prague Newsroom , 420 - 2 - 2423 - 0003 
